cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with 3D pose estimation of human hands using CNNs and depth cameras. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training a hierarchical tree-like structured CNN, which can be related to robotics and control (cs.RO). The use of end-to-end training and loss function design can be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Lastly, the paper involves modeling joints correlations and dependencies, which can be related to computer graphics (cs.GR).
